Rules.InvariantScript: "Search by Description, Pack title or Code"

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
If(
    LookUp(
        'Item Masters',
        'Item Master' = LookUp(
            'SKU Masters',
            'SKU Master' = ThisItem.'SKU Master'
        ).'Item Code'.'Item Master'
    ).UOM = 'UOM (Item Masters)'.CASE,
    DisplayMode.Edit,
    DisplayMode.Disabled
)

Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    varLoading || LookUp(
        'SKU Masters',
        'SKU Master' = ThisItem.'SKU Master'
    ).'Product group code' = 'Product group code (Choice)'.'2WAY',
    DisplayMode.Disabled,
    DisplayMode.Edit
)

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
If(
    LookUp(
        'Item Masters',
        'Item Master' = LookUp(
            'SKU Masters',
            'SKU Master' = ThisItem.'SKU Master'
        ).'Item Code'.'Item Master'
    ).UOM = 'UOM (Item Masters)'.PCS,
    DisplayMode.Edit,
    DisplayMode.Disabled
)

Rules.InvariantScript: If(IsBlank(LookUp(colReasonsVisits, id = ThisItem.'SKU Master').reason), false, true)
If(!IsBlank(LookUp(colReasonsVisits, id = ThisItem.'SKU Master').reason), false, true)
Filter( 'SKU Masters', txtSearchInput_1.Text in 'SKU Code' || txtSearchInput_1.Text in 'Item Description ' || txtSearchInput_1.Text in 'Pack Title')

If(
    varVisitReturnOrMenuReturn,
    If(
        IsBlank(colReasonsVisits) || IsBlank(VarReplaceCustomerName) || IsBlank(Label8_3),
        DisplayMode.Disabled,
        DisplayMode.Edit
    ),
    If(
        IsBlank(colReasonsVisits) && IsBlank(txtReturnOrderDataPcsValue) && IsBlank(Label8_3),
        DisplayMode.Disabled,
        DisplayMode.Edit
    )
)

If(
    varVisitReturnOrMenuReturn,
    If(
        IsBlank(colReasonsVisits) || IsBlank(VarReplaceCustomerName) || IsBlank(Label8_3),
        DisplayMode.Disabled,
        DisplayMode.Edit
    ),
    If(
        IsBlank(colReasonsVisits) && IsBlank(txtReturnOrderDataPcsValue) && IsBlank(Label8_3),
        DisplayMode.Disabled,
        DisplayMode.Edit
    )
)
